                Consider Shopping Clearance
                Shop our men’s clothing clearance to add those extra pieces to your wardrobe.

                If the gaps in your wardrobe are becoming more apparent every time an important business or social function approaches, it might be time to think about new options. That’s the beauty of shopping the men’s clothing clearance at Men’s Wearhouse. With over 1,000 items typically included, both in-store and online, the selection is unrivaled. The values are exceptional as well and they liberate a man who appreciates great style to add versatility to his closet. It’s a great way to fill out your seasonal needs or simply to provide more possibilities for spontaneous mixing and matching. Our clearance selection consists of suits, sport coats, dress shirts, jeans, ties, shoes and outerwear. Everything on clearance is permanently marked down with savings of 30 percent to 70 percent off retail prices. And unlike clearance offerings at other clothiers, our choices aren’t limited to overstocked, outdated and out-of-season items. Many times we simply need to create room for refreshed inventory for the season at hand. That means you’ll find items you can wear right away, and a surprisingly wide range of sizes, too. Keeping an eye on our clearance is a smart strategy to discover great styles from leading designers like Calvin Klein, Kenneth Cole, Egara and more, while getting a jump on the pieces that’ll set you up to look better than ever next season. And we’re adding new items to our clearance selection every month, so it makes sense to check back often.
